{"name":"AOP","postlist":[{"title":"AspectJ","slug":"AspectJ","date":"2018-03-27T06:33:19.000Z","updated":"2018-04-08T06:51:36.017Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/AspectJ.json","excerpt":"如果说，OOP 如果是把问题划分到单个模块的话，那么 AOP 就是把涉及到众多模块的某一类问题进行统一管理。这里通过几个小例子，讲解在 Android 开发中，如何运用 AOP 的方式，进行全局切片管理，达到简洁优雅，一劳永逸的效果。","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":null,"raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"程序设计","path":"api/categories/程序设计.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Android","path":"api/tags/Android.json"},{"name":"AOP","path":"api/tags/AOP.json"},{"name":"AspectJ","path":"api/tags/AspectJ.json"}]},{"title":"Android AOP","slug":"Android AOP","date":"2018-03-16T06:28:19.000Z","updated":"2018-04-08T06:51:21.151Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Android AOP.json","excerpt":"Android AOP 就是通过预编译方式和运行期动态代理实现程序功能的统一维护的一种技术。利用 AOP 可以对业务逻辑的各个部分进行隔离，从而使得业务逻辑各部分之间的耦合度降低，提高程序的可重用性，提高开发效率。","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":null,"raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"程序设计","path":"api/categories/程序设计.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Android","path":"api/tags/Android.json"},{"name":"AOP","path":"api/tags/AOP.json"}]}]}